\c 15 Ndiani angagara mutende raJehovha? 151 Jehovha, ndianiko angatsaukira mutende renyu? Ndianiko angagara pagomo renyu dzvene? 2 Uyo, anofamba asina mhosva, anoita zvakarurama, Anotaura zvokwadi mumwoyo make. 3 Iye asina makuhwa parurimi rwake, Asingaitiri shamwari yake zvakaipa, Asingatuki waagere naye. 4 Munhu akashata anozvidzwa naye; Asi anokudza vanotya Jehovha. Iye anoti kana achinge apika, haangazoshanduri shoko rake,
